tags.description: Tasmania's coolest locale. Settle by the fire in the snowy, luxe interior of marble and plush grey leather at Institut Polaire. Sip on an Antarctic dry gin martini, savour new wave Tasmanian pinot noir or nurse your single malt.
tags.name: Institut Polaire
